      "raw_text": "A number of improvements will\nbe made at North Yakima this\nyear by the Northern Pacific COM\npany An icehouse that will hold\n5000 tons is now being erected in\nthe lower yards. A new freight\nwarehouse 60 by $50 feet in size\nwill also be built soon just north\nOF the present one. $4,000 feet of\nnew track will also be built."
